==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*μαρτύριον / marturion / mar-too'-ree-on

===Etymology===
*Neuter of a presumed derivative of [[μάρτυς]] {{GG|3144}}; something evidential, that is, (generally) evidence given or (specifically) the Decalogue (in the sacred Tabernacle):  

===Noun===
'''μαρτύριον'''

# To be testified, [[testimony]], [[witness]].

